The Biggest Loser Australia - Families Season 10 Episode 03

Hosted by Fiona Falkiner, this season of TBL Families will see the trainers each paired with one Aussie family of four, as they motivate them to achieve their weight-loss dreams.

After living with the four TBL families for the past week, it is time for the trainers to weigh-in. The results leave them, and their families, shocked
